        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "$1 / 0.8 = 1.25$."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Simplify $\\sec^2 x - \\tan^2 x$.",
        "options": ["$1$", "$0$", "$-1$", "$\\sec x$"],
        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "This is a fundamental Pythagorean identity."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "The angle of depression from a cliff to a boat is $30^\\circ$. If the cliff is 100m high, find the distance to the boat.",
