        "explanation": "$\\cos x \\cos \\pi + \\sin x \\sin \\pi = \\cos x(-1) + 0 = -\\cos x$."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Evaluate $\\tan(0)$ using the difference formula $\\tan(x - x)$.",
