        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "$\\sin(2\\theta) = 2\\sin\\theta\\cos\\theta = 2(0.4) = 0.8$."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Simplify $2\\sin^2(x/2) - 1$.",
        "options": ["$-\\cos x$", "$\\cos x$", "$\\sin x$", "$-\\sin x$"],
        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "Using $\\cos(2A) = 1 - 2\\sin^2 A$, let $A = x/2$."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Rewrite $\\sin(5x) - \\sin(3x)$ as a product.",
