        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "$2\\cos((5x+3x)/2)\\sin((5x-3x)/2) = 2\\cos(4x)\\sin(x)$."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Solve $\\cos^2 x = 0$ for $x \\in [0, 2\\pi)$.",
