        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "Tangent is $-1$ in the second quadrant at $3\\pi/4$."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Find the area of a triangle with $a=6, c=10$ and $B=30^\\circ$.",
